title: Costco membership worldwide 2014 to 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Total number of card holders. In total the number of data points it has is 6.
Overall Total number of card holders has increased over the Year.
Total number of card holders is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2019.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2015 and 2016.
The highest Total number of card holders, of value 98.5 was reached at Year 2019
Minimum Total number of card holders about 76.4 was reached at Year 2014
